query:
SELECT pr.id, pr.pickingOrderId, pr.productId, pr.quantity, p.sku, p.description, i.batch 
FROM pickingReservations pr 
LEFT JOIN inventory i ON pr.inventoryId = i.id 
LEFT JOIN products p ON pr.productId = p.id 
LEFT JOIN warehouseLocations wl ON i.locationId = wl.id 
WHERE wl.code = 'EXP-01-A';
